## Cost & Licensing

- **Microsoft 365 Business with Copilot — new SKU launching July 1.** Microsoft is introducing new small-business SKUs with Copilot built in. Organizations currently purchasing Microsoft 365 Business Standard/Premium plus a separate Copilot license should review whether consolidating to the new SKU changes their total cost. IT and procurement teams should evaluate before July 1 renewals.
- **Work IQ API — pay-as-you-go consumption launching June 2026.** Developers and partners can now access Copilot's underlying intelligence APIs on a metered basis without pre-assigned licenses. Organizations building custom agents or integrations should understand this creates a new consumption-billed cost vector that needs budget visibility and governance.
- **Microsoft 365 adds advanced Intune solutions at scale (rolling out Q3 CY2026).** Microsoft 365 E3/E5 plans are adding advanced Intune Suite capabilities. Organizations currently paying for the Intune Suite as a separate add-on should work with their licensing advisor to determine whether their existing agreement provides these capabilities at no additional cost once the rollout occurs. A 30-day Message Center notice will precede tenant activation.
- **Exchange 2016/2019 ESU Period 2 now available.** Organizations that have not yet migrated to Exchange Subscription Edition can enroll in the Period 2 Extended Security Update program (May 2026 through October 2026). This is a paid program — organizations should evaluate whether ESU cost is preferable to accelerating migration, given that ESU ends and the migration cost does not decrease over time.
- **Purview DLP for Copilot now included.** Microsoft Purview Data Loss Prevention for Microsoft 365 Copilot and Copilot Chat prompts is now generally available and included at no additional cost for all Microsoft 365 Copilot and Copilot Chat licensed users. Organizations that have been deferring DLP configuration for Copilot interactions should activate this now — there is no licensing barrier.

*Sources: [Microsoft 365 Blog — Business with Copilot SKU](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/blog/2026/05/28/introducing-microsoft-365-business-with-copilot-the-new-standard-for-small-business/) · [M365 Roadmap — Work IQ Pay-As-You-Go](https://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-365/roadmap?id=559017) · [Intune Blog — Advanced Solutions at Scale](https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/microsoft-intune-blog/microsoft-365-adds-advanced-microsoft-intune-solutions-at-scale/ba-p/4474272) · [Security Community — DLP for Copilot GA](https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/microsoft-security-community/safeguarding-sensitive-data-in-microsoft-365-copilot/ba-p/4512497)*

